  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWhen running our validator client with multiple validators, our validator client spams the beacon node with repeated requests that could be batched\r\n\r\n```\r\n2021-03-23 15:00:00 [API]             debug: Request: 127.0.0.1 -> 127.0.0.1:9596\tGET:/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators/0x810c608e7eda878ac8bed378f6e29504698422345895b74eb40717e5501a5b554d2e19b2e468fcd9ec05131ad4db557e\tRequestId: 18275\r\n2021-03-23 15:00:00 [API]             debug: Request: 127.0.0.1 -> 127.0.0.1:9596\tGET:/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators/0x8136274d1fe87eb017d1e9a7ad36b35014d71601241100688f06c6b64d1ada508b97b2f8b54b79076360a9ecf735c5a0\tRequestId: 18276\r\n2021-03-23 15:00:00 [API]             debug: Request: 127.0.0.1 -> 127.0.0.1:9596\tGET:/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators/0x81d4b7ca812383c670abb67ce04dddaa6b378dda7144869f4fa69d7fde47a12199e2eca3231d2aa1884b78c9721b45ef\tRequestId: 18277\r\n2021-03-23 15:00:00 [API]             debug: Request: 127.0.0.1 -> 127.0.0.1:9596\tGET:/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/validators/0x82744af45bbb63fd5b74e0e6bec230b02ffc39972180232ae830b9ef535faaf534eaf6d1bf8f273b5c56d4d62b316c93\tRequestId: 18278\r\n```\r\n\r\nAlso for\r\n```\r\nPOST:/eth/v1/validator/beacon_committee_subscriptions\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd probably more\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nvalidator client should be smarter and batch the requests\r\n",
